title: Jordan Granville Pro SP
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: What's your go-to? A fresh addition to the 23 Engineered line, the Granville Pro swoops in and delivers big on the concept of 24/7. Pairing innovation with off-court DNA, a cushy Formula 23 midsole brings the comfort. The upper sports a throwback mix of materials inspired by MJ's university days, from classic suede to laser-cut textile and airy mesh. Exposed foam on the tongue and a sporty heel clip add retro-futuristic flair, while hidden details (check out the tongue label text and "23" molded into the outsole) add clout. Whether you're chilling with friends, heading to the office, or lacing up for a big night out—the Granville Pro has you covered.

title: Jordan 1 Mid Sneaker School
subtitle: Little Kids' Shoes

subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: One of history's most iconic sneakers takes on a new shine to celebrate 75 years of the NBA. A diamond border on the tongue label nod to the NBA's diamond anniversary, making a fresh play on an all-time favorite.

title: Jordan Series .02 "Dear Dean"
subtitle: Shoes
short_description: Dean Smith was like a father to MJ. The legendary coach helped transform Mike's dogfight mentality and the determination he’d learned from Larry into greatness on the collegiate basketball court. The vulcanized Jordan Series .02 "Dear Dean" continues the story of how Mike became the greatest of all time. Wearable in any setting, it's also got some stretch to accommodate wider feet. The shoe symbolizes the influence and inspiration for generations of kids who look up to Mike—just like Mike looked up to Coach Smith.

title: Jordan 'Why Not?' Zer0.4

Cue the Jordan 'Why Not?' Zer0.4, the first to feature double-stacked Zoom in the forefoot. It's an extra-responsive cushioning system that's designed to help him transform speed into force and focus his attack.

title: Zion 1 SP
subtitle: Men's Basketball Shoes
short_description: Pairing a down-to-earth persona with out-of-this-world athleticism, Zion brings his best to the game—and he's got footwear to match. His shoes are light, stable and strong, with a durable outsole that grips the court. Meanwhile, Air cushioning provides the plush underfoot comfort and rapid responsiveness you know and love.

subtitle: Little Kids' Shoes

title: Zion 1 "Gen Zion"
subtitle: Basketball Shoes
short_description: One clip was all it took for what was happening in a small high school gymnasium to command the attention of the entire world. But it didn’t stop with one clip, soon becoming endless highlights reels of athletic defiance and impossibility, ignited by fire emojis and fueled by infinite retweets. Jumping out of the gym after full days of school, Zion quickly became the face of Gen Z, crowned with a blue checkmark and front-page articles dubbing him the future of basketball. Inspired by the virality of his gameplay, “Gen Zion” celebrates Zion’s ascension to the spotlight and representation of the next generation of the game.

The lower collar height allows ankle mobility while keeping you fully and comfortably contained. This PF version has an extra-durable outsole that's ideal for outdoor courts.

short_description: You've got the hops and the speed—lace up in shoes that enhance what you bring to the court. The latest AJ is all about takeoffs and landings, with multiple Air units to get you off the ground and our signature Formula 23 foam to cushion your impact. Up top, you'll find layers of tough, reinforced leno-weave fabric that'll keep you contained—and leave your game uncompromised—no matter how fast you move.

title: Air Jordan 1 Elevate Low SE
subtitle: Women's Shoe
short_description: Rise to the occasion in style that soars. This shoe reworks an icon's original magic with a platform sole and low cut silhouette. Air cushioning keeps you lifted, and sleek leather in contrasting colors adds visual interest.

title: Air Jordan 2 Retro Low Titan
subtitle: Shoes
short_description: Spread the love. Tell the stories. Step into greatness. Teaming up with Filipino basketball collective, Titan, this timeless take on the AJ2 bridges past, present and future. With an unquestionable passion for the game, designer Chi Loyzaga-Gibbs sets the stage with an honorary look that's rooted to the beloved 1954 Filipino national team. Premium suede, richly textured corduroy and crisp leather combine with a speckled midsole, while original artwork connects you to the hoops heartbeat no matter where you are.

title: Air Jordan 1 Mid
subtitle: Shoes
short_description: Inspired by the original AJ1, the Air Jordan 1 Mid offers fans a chance to follow in MJ's footsteps. Fresh color trims the clean, classic materials, imbuing modernity into a classic design.

title: Air Jordan 7 Retro SE
subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
short_description: Kick it back to '92 with this latest iteration of the AJ7, reviving the championship legacy for a new generation of sneakerheads. Come for the throwback style, stay all day for the premium construction and signature Air cushioning.

title: Zion 2
subtitle: Baby/Toddler Shoes
short_description: Prep your future pro with a pint-sized version of the Zion 2. An adjustable strap helps support little feet when a young athlete is hard at play—and makes 'em easier to take off when the game is over.

title: Jordan Delta 3 Low SP
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: Play hard, look good, speak your truth. Celebrating the power of unity with a dose of Parisian flair, these shoes showcase the multiverse of what it means to be "woman." Super plush comfort and an adventurous mix of materials come together for a look that kicks stereotypes to the curb. The pattern on the laces was created for the Jordan Women's Paris Collective apparel collection, honoring the community leaders at the heart of the designs.

title: Air Jordan 11 CMFT Low
subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
short_description: Get comfy in the Air Jordan 11 CMFT Low. Inspired by classic Jordan sneakers, this low-top shoe has a soft leather toe and webbing lace loops for quick lacing. Underfoot is soft, smooth foam with rubber pods in just the right spots for traction.

title: Zion 2
subtitle: Baby/Toddler Shoes
short_description: Prep your future pro with a pint-sized version of the Zion 2. An adjustable strap helps support little feet when a young athlete is hard at play—and makes 'em easier to take off when the game is over.

title: Jordan 6 Rings
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Celebrate the legendary career of "His Airness" with the Jordan 6 Rings. Incorporating key features of each shoe worn during the championship series, it has premium details and lightweight, low-profile Zoom Air cushioning that delivers a responsive feel underfoot.

title: Sky Jordan 1
subtitle: Little Kids' Shoe
short_description: Inspired by the AJ1, the Sky Jordan 1 is equal parts iconic and adorable. It has soft foam cushioning, rubber traction and a hook-and-loop strap for easy on and off.

title: Jordan 1 Mid SE
subtitle: Baby/Toddler Shoes
short_description: These baby J's combine an iconic design with fresh new colors. They're soft and flexible underfoot, easy to get on, and comfortable to wear all day.

title: Jordan Air 200E
subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
TopColor: Summit White/Light Smoke Grey/Wild Berry/Coconut Milk
short_description: These kicks are designed for up-and-coming sneakerheads with big ideas. A bold mix of colors and materials makes a splash, while the see-through Max Air unit embraces futuristic design. Use the handy pull tabs to get your shoes on without missing a beat and zip through your day in comfort.
color-Description: Summit White/Light Smoke Grey/Wild Berry/Coconut Milk

title: Jordan One Take II
subtitle: Big Kids' Basketball Shoes
short_description: Russell Westbrook backs up his brashness with a fast, aggressive playing style and numbers that can't be ignored. His all-new Jordan One Take II embodies his quickness. Colors, textures and design lines speak to Russ' persona both on and off the court.

title: Jordan Delta 2 SP
subtitle: Shoes
short_description: The Jordan Delta 2 offers a fresh, fearless take on the features you want: durability, comfort and an attitude that's Jordan to the core. We updated design lines and swapped out some components, but the idea is the same as the first Delta. The 2 still has that clashing combination of supportive and space age-like materials, with lots of different textures and heavy stitching to create a look that's both adventurous and iconic.

title: Jordan Play Luka
subtitle: Men's Slides
short_description: From walking the dog to hanging out courtside, these essential slides have you covered. Bright colors and an imaginative pattern celebrate Luka's bold moves while thick, lightweight foam supports your feet comfortably.

title: Jordan 8 Retro
subtitle: Baby/Toddler Shoes
short_description: Your little one might not know that MJ got his 3rd career title in these shoes—but they're still gonna look great rockin' em. Season-ready hues and patterns energize the classic shoe for a new generation of mini sneakerheads.

title: Jordan 1 Mid
subtitle: Little Kids' Shoes
short_description: Sneaker school is officially in session. Made with dry erase patent leather, these kicks are a walking whiteboard—all they need is your little one's creative touch. Get out the dry erase markers and observe every bold squiggle, line, and curve. When they're done designing, easily wipe them clean, leaving nothing but a blank canvas and a stylized Swoosh.

title: Luka 1
subtitle: Men's Basketball Shoes
short_description: Designed for #77 and made for every athlete craving speed and efficiency, Luka's debut delivers the goods. The first shoe with full-length Formula 23 foam, it has an ultra-supportive fit crafted with the step-back in mind. Meanwhile, strong and lightweight Flight Wire cables keep you feeling contained, whether you're playing indoors or out. This is the assist you've been waiting for—get out there and make your shot.

title: Jumpman Two Trey
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: Ride high in kicks created to honor MJ's time in Chicago. Genuine leather and classic Air cushioning combine for a premium look and feel. Who are you reppin'? Two Trey, baby.

title: Air Jordan XXXVII Tatum
subtitle: Men's Basketball Shoes
short_description: You've got the hops and the speed—lace up in shoes that enhance what you bring to the court. The latest AJ is all about takeoffs and landings, with multiple Air units to get you off the ground and our signature Formula 23 foam to cushion your impact. Up top, you'll find layers of tough, reinforced leno-weave fabric that'll keep you contained—and your game uncompromised—no matter how fast you move.

title: Jordan Delta 3 SP
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Combining high-end craft with high-tech features, these kicks are the embodiment of cool. Airy ripstop and soft suede pair with a soft interior for a classic look and premium Jordan Brand comfort.

title: Air Jordan XXXVI SE
subtitle: Basketball Shoe
short_description: Breaking barriers and making history as the first Japanese-born player to be a first-round draft pick is just the start for Rui Hachimura. With the world’s biggest games in his home country for the first time in over 50 years, Rui knows he’s here for a reason. Inspired by all of the places Rui can take basketball, the Air Jordan XXXVI SE “Black Samurai” celebrates the purpose and pride that comes with repping your country’s colors.

title: Air Jordan XXXV Luka
subtitle: Big Kids' Basketball Shoes
short_description: Out on the court, it's a point guard, it's a no-look pass wizard...no, it's Luka Dončić, aka Wonderboy! His Air Jordan XXXV helps him feel ultralight, fast, and low to the ground. It's built around a sleek, sculpted midsole plate that's hollowed out to help reduce weight. Springy Zoom Air cushioning under the heel and forefoot provides nonstop responsiveness for ballers who're inspired by Luka's game.

title: Air Jordan 1 Mid
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: The Air Jordan 1 Mid brings full-court style and premium comfort to an iconic look. Its Air-Sole unit cushions play on the hardwood, while the padded collar gives you a supportive feel.

title: Air Jordan 1 Low SE
subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
short_description: Inspired by the original that debuted in 1985, these low-profile J's are always fresh. Dress 'em up or dress 'em down—their good looks and plush comfort will never go out of style.

title: Jordan 1 Mid SE
subtitle: Little Kids' Shoes
short_description: Get that Jordan energy on their feet this holiday season. Rich grain leather with bright details make little feet shine like holiday lights. It's soft and flexible underfoot, easy to get on, and comfortable to wear all day.

title: Jordan 1 Mid SE
subtitle: Little Kids' Shoes
short_description: Celebrate your little all-star with these AJ1s. Metallic leather and bold colors add shimmer and shine to all their off-court looks.

title: Jordan Proto-Max 720
subtitle: Shoes
short_description: Inspired by outer space flight, the Jordan Proto-Max 720 provides all-day comfort with a future-forward look. An outer shroud covers the sock-like bootie construction, while Nike Air cushions every step.

title: Jordan Break
subtitle: Big Kids' Slides
short_description: The Jordan Break Slide is lightweight and comfortable with a soft foam footbed and strap that conform to your foot. It’s easy to slip on after practice or when you’re heading out the door.

title: Air Jordan 13 Retro
subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
short_description: The Air Jordan 13 Retro has been a longtime favorite among fans and collectors. It's got the recognizable side panels, a holographic logo, plus the outsole that resembles a panther's paw. Comfortable cushioning and a mix of leather, synthetic and textile materials in the upper give it a fresh look and feel.

title: Jordan Delta 2
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: The Jordan Delta 2 offers a fresh, fearless take on the features you want: durability, comfort and an attitude that's Jordan to the core. We updated design lines and swapped out some components, but the idea is the same as the first Delta. The 2 still has that clashing combination of supportive and space age-like materials, with lots of different textures and heavy stitching to create a look that's both adventurous and iconic.

title: Air Jordan 1 Low
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Inspired by the original that debuted in 1985, the Air Jordan 1 Low offers a clean, classic look that's familiar yet always fresh. With an iconic design that pairs perfectly with any 'fit, these kicks ensure you'll always be on point.

title: Zion 2
subtitle: Little Kids' Shoes
short_description: Prep your future pro with a pint-sized version of the Zion 2. An adjustable strap helps support little feet when young athletes are hard at play—and makes 'em easier to take off when the game is over.

title: Jordan LS
subtitle: Slides
short_description: Fresh and functional, the Jordan LS Slide offers step-in comfort. It has an adjustable fold-over strap built on a Solarsoft foam footbed, plus a removable heel strap to personalize your fit. A removable stash pocket ups the utility.

title: Jordan Break
subtitle: Slides
short_description: Featuring a fixed strap over the top of the foot, the Jordan Break Slide uses durable synthetic leather and lightweight foam cushioning for underfoot comfort.

title: Jordan Hydro XI Retro
subtitle: Men's Slide
short_description: The Jordan Hydro XI Retro Men's Slide is designed with a soft, textured footbed and flexible sole for lasting comfort.

title: Air Jordan 1 Low SE
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: Stand out to fit in. It's the classic AJ1 look you love, made special for summer with sky blue leather, a fun speckled sole and crisp white canvas. The embroidered Wings logo on the heel adds a premium finish.

title: Jordan MA2
subtitle: Little Kids' Shoes
short_description: The Jordan MA2 makes plays on the playground with bold details and a fun mix of materials. With a foam midsole, Max Air in the heel. and a lightweight upper, it's comfortable from top to bottom.

title: Jordan 1 Mid SE
subtitle: Baby/Toddler Shoes
short_description: Bring your kiddo into sneaker culture with these scaled-down J's modeled after Michael Jordan's signature classic. The Jordan 1 Mid SE combines patterned knit materials with sturdy leather overlays, making it light, supportive, and fun.

title: Air Jordan 1 Hi FlyEase
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: The Air Jordan 1 Hi FlyEase combines the coveted style of Michael Jordan's first signature sneaker with a quick and easy one-handed entry system. There are no laces to tie, just a wraparound zipper and two straps to secure a custom fit.

title: Air Jordan 2 Retro Low SP
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Spread the love. Tell the stories. Step into greatness. Our collab with South Africa’s leading sneaker and streetwear store Shelflife is a fresh take on the AJ2, grounding you to the spirit of TEAM ONLY (just check out the back of the tongue). Rooted to Shelflife's graffiti and street art origins, the design serves blank canvas symbolism with its neutral upper. Bright accents boost the energy while insole graphics—a collage of signatures and autographs from the Shelflife community—evoke the company's ethos: "It's only through our team that we become who we are."

title: Air Jordan 1 Low SE
subtitle: Women's Shoe
short_description: Serving straight-up cozy vibes, Air Jordan 1 Low SE gets comfy. The soft pink accents bring a pop of freshness and highlight its iconic features, made with a combo of jersey, canvas, and mesh material.

title: Jordan 1 Mid SE
subtitle: Baby/Toddler Shoes
short_description: Made with premium leather and soft, flexible cushioning, the Jordan 1 Mid SE is durably built and comfortable to wear all day—great for little ones who want to keep up with the big kids.

title: Jordan MA2
subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
short_description: The all-new Jordan MA2 makes plays on the street with wildly diverse materials. Varied designs create a look that captures a look of Jordan heritage while forging a fresh, new identity that stands on its own.

title: Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 39 Shield
subtitle: Men's Weatherized Road Running Shoes
short_description: Your workhorse with wings returns to help you push through the rain. A water-repellent finish helps keep you dry while a cozy fleece-like feel on the inside helps keep your feet warm for nasty-weather runs. Rugged traction and 2 Zoom Air units provide grip and soft cushioning, so you can power through the elements.

title: Nike Free Run 5.0
subtitle: Men's Road Running Shoes
short_description: Made from at least 20% recycled material by weight, the sock-like boot of this Nike Free is designed to transition from running to training to your everyday routine. With a breathable knit upper, it combines the flexibility you love with a secure design that will help keep you close to the ground for that barefoot feeling. New cushioning is lighter, softer and more responsive than previous versions so you can keep moving in comfort whether you’re on the pavement or track.

title: Nike Air Zoom Alphafly NEXT% 2
subtitle: Men's Road Racing Shoes
short_description: Once you take a few strides in the Nike Air Zoom Alphafly NEXT% 2, you’ll never look at your favorite pair of old racing shoes the same way again. These rocket ships are made to help shave precious time off your personal records without surrendering the foundation you need to go the full distance. A thick, lightweight support system marries the 2 worlds of comfort and speed in holy running matrimony. Enjoy the greatest energy return of all our racing shoes while you chase your personal bests.

title: Nike Zoom Fly 5
subtitle: Men's Road Running Shoes
short_description: Bridge the gap between your weekend training run and race day in a durable design that can be deployed not just at the starting line of your favorite race but in the days and months after your conquest. It offers comfort and reliability but with a propulsive sensation that’ll help you feel fast and fresh. That kind of versatility is uncommon in the running arena. But who said you can’t have it all?

title: Nike Winflo 8 Shield
subtitle: Men's Weatherized Road Running Shoes
short_description: Gear up for rainy runs with weatherized support to match your speed. Air Zoom units give soft cushioning for maximum comfort, with a neutral feel that helps lessen the chance of stress-related injuries. Plus, tire-inspired soles offer tough traction for grip that keeps you running on slick streets. Bonded seams help keep water out so you can hit your winter goals with confidence.

title: Nike Free Run 5.0 Next Nature
subtitle: Women's Road Running Shoes
short_description: Perfect for when you want it to be just you and your run. The Nike Free Run 5.0 Next Nature strips away what’s not essential, leaving you free to concentrate on your stride and the landscape around you. The breathable knit upper and low-cut design provide flexibility and stability while lightweight foam underfoot gives you the comfortable cushioning you need to power through your route.

short_description: The Nike Air Zoom Terra Kiger 8 keeps it light and tight. It's a no-frills shoe built with only what you need, for a secure fit and feel. We made it to help keep your foot in place, so you stay agile and upright over uneven terrain. Plus, it's got the soft cushioning and responsive feel that gives you a little extra spring with every step. So strap in and get ready to run through the mud and with the trail.

title: Nike ZoomX Zegama
subtitle: Men's Trail Running Shoes
short_description: Navigate the up and downs of uncompromising terrain with the Nike ZoomX Zegama. Developed with great grip and stability, it has you covered so you can keep climbing and reach greater personal heights when the going gets grimy and gritty. Whether it's a challenging, rocky landscape going uphill or a steep, slick decline down a treacherous trail, feel confident when you decide to off-road it.

title: Nike Quest 4
subtitle: Women's Road Running Shoes
short_description: The pursuit of speed continues with the Nike Quest 4. Take on the streets with higher foam heights and cushioned comfort that combine with a lightweight upper to offer secure support. Intuitive details make it a staple for the everyday runner.

title: Nike Alphafly NEXT% 2
subtitle: Women's Road Racing Shoes
short_description: Once you take a few strides in the Nike Alphafly NEXT% 2, you’ll never look at your favorite pair of old racing shoes the same way again. These rocket ships are made to help shave precious time off your personal records without surrendering the foundation you need to go the full distance. A thick, lightweight support system marries the 2 worlds of comfort and speed in holy running matrimony. Enjoy the greatest energy return of all our racing shoes while you chase your personal bests and leave the competition in the dust.

title: Nike React Pegasus Trail 4
subtitle: Men's Trail Running Shoes
short_description: Running is your daily ritual, taking you from road to trail as you seek out new adventures and goals. Let the Nike React Pegasus Trail 4 take you there and back again with its supportive and springy feel. Underfoot traction keeps you going over rocky terrain, while still providing a smooth ride for the road. Midfoot support is controlled by the laces, letting you find the right fit and feel. Your trusted workhorse with wings is ready for an off-road journey. Time to fly.

title: Nike Flex Runner 2 Lil
subtitle: Baby/Toddler Shoes
short_description: Your future racers will love exploring the outdoors in the Nike Flex Runner 2. As part of our Lil collection (meaning, just for little ones), these shoes encourage discovery and play through nature. Unearth all the things we love about these, like the cute rabbit and mushroom graphics. Can your little adventurer identify them all?

title: Nike React Infinity Run Flyknit 2
subtitle: Women's Road Running Shoes
short_description: The Nike React Infinity Run Flyknit 2 continues to help keep you running. A refreshed upper combines Flyknit and Flywire technology for support and breathability where you need it. A wider forefoot provides stability to prevent rolling, while the high foam heights provide soft responsiveness and long-lasting comfort. It's still one of our most tested shoes, designed to help you feel the potential when your foot hits the pavement.

title: Nike React Phantom Run Flyknit 2
subtitle: Men's Running Shoes
short_description: Inspired by the vibrant energy and sights that take place during a color run, the Nike React Phantom Run Flyknit 2 brings those electrifying feels to your feet. Building on the foundation of its predecessor, these shoes expand on their laceless design by adding secure support that feels like it "disappears" on your foot. More foam means better cushioning, keeping you comfortable as you run.

title: Nike Experience Run 11 Next Nature
subtitle: Men's Road Running Shoes
short_description: Comfortably zen, just like every run should be. With the Nike Experience Run 11 Next Nature, we created a lightweight, clean design that feels as good as it looks. Plus, they're made with at least 20% recycled content by weight, keeping us on our sustainability journey.

subtitle: Men's Road Running Shoes
short_description: Take your training runs to the next level with the Nike Air Zoom Pegasus 37. With unbelievable React cushioning and a new forefoot Air unit, they’re like a bolt of caffeine for your legs. The lightweight upper breathes incredibly well. Pared-down, perfectly placed padding helps reduce hotspots. And the super grippy outsole? Well, let’s just say you gotta stay upright to run. Here’s to letting mud fly and streets vanish behind you.

title: Nike ZoomX Invincible Run Flyknit 2
subtitle: Women's Road Running Shoes
short_description: Keep pushing your runs to the limit. The Nike ZoomX Invincible Run Flyknit 2 keeps you going with the same super-soft feel that lets you feel the potential when your foot hits the pavement. We created the shoe with plenty of springy responsiveness and incredible support to help keep you feeling secure and competitive. It's one of our most tested shoes, still designed for you to stay on the road and away from the sidelines.

Higher foam provides soft responsiveness and long-lasting comfort, plus a wider forefoot helps lessen the chance of stress-related injuries. It's still 1 of our most tested shoes, designed to help you feel the potential when your foot hits the pavement.

subtitle: Men's Weatherized Road Running Shoes

title: Nike Air Zoom Terra Kiger 8
subtitle: Men's Trail Running Shoes
short_description: The Nike Air Zoom Terra Kiger 8 keeps it light and tight. It's a no-frills shoe built with only what you need, for a secure fit and feel. We made it to help keep your foot in place, so you stay agile and upright over uneven terrain. Plus, it's got the soft cushioning and responsive feel that gives you a little extra spring with every step. So strap in and get ready to run through the mud and with the trail.

title: Nike Escape Run Flyknit
subtitle: Women's Road Running Shoes
short_description: The streets are your playground. Enjoy all they have to offer in the Nike Escape Run Flyknit. Hit the ground running with Nike React foam for a responsive, durable ride. Stretchy, secure materials, plus plush foam underfoot give comfort that keeps the pace. Busy sidewalks are no problems with multidirectional traction that helps provide stability for unexpected obstacles. Lace up, it's time to escape.

subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes

title: Nike Zoom Rival
subtitle: Track & Field Sprinting Spikes
short_description: Race out of the starting blocks and finish with a flurry in a spike designed with speed in mind. Its robust, reinforced yet lightweight upper provides the key containment necessary to attack the turns and straightaways around the oval. Feel the power and drive of the forefoot plate as you get up on your toes and hightail it toward the tape.

Your trusted workhorse with wings is back—time to fly.

subtitle: Men's Road Running Shoes
short_description: The Vomero 16 adds responsive ZoomX foam cushioning, bringing an energetic pop to your stride that’s perfect for high mileage on the road. It’s super lightweight, with plenty of stretch and ventilation through the upper. Looking for the right amount of support? We’ve got you covered with an adjustable midfoot band and a stable clip at the heel.

title: Nike Air Zoom Pegasus FlyEase
subtitle: Men's Easy On/Off Road Running Shoes
short_description: Let the Nike Air Zoom Pegasus FlyEase help you ascend to new heights. Designed to offer a balanced and energized ride for any run, they provide a supportive sensation that helps your foot feel contained. Plus, Nike FlyEase technology acts as a strap, helping secure your fit and making these easy to take on and off. Zoom Air units in the forefoot and heel help add a pop to your stride as you transition from heel to toe while bursts of bright colors throughout the sleek black upper bring fresh energy to your run. Your trusted workhorse with wings is back. Time to fly.

title: Nike Renew Serenity Run 2
subtitle: Women's Road Running Shoes
short_description: Unwind and enjoy the journey ahead with neutral running shoes made for the moments when your steps speed up to help ease your mind. Plush, lightweight cushioning complement a fit that'll help you stayed focused on seeking the joy in the journey. Quiet the world around you while you run, putting today's troubles in the past while letting tomorrow worry about itself.

subtitle: Big Kids' Running Shoes

subtitle: Little Kids' Shoes

title: Nike Explor Next Nature
subtitle: Baby/Toddler Shoes
short_description: Thoughtfully designed with at least 20% recycled material by weight, we reimagined running shoes without sacrificing kid-right comfort. Lightweight foam on the heel, a cushiony material made from foam material and Nike Grind rubber (recycled scraps that show up as speckles.) Innovative, cushioned and just plain awesome to wear from the track to the playground.

title: Nike Dynamo GO SE
subtitle: Little Kids' Easy On/Off Shoes
short_description: Follow the trail of pawprints left by your little critter when they rock the Nike Dynamo GO. What we love most is how easy these are for kiddos to put on. Little feet can stomp down on the collapsible heel and then slide into the shoe with ease, helping them learn to be independent. Once they're on, let kids imagine themselves as their favorite animal as they go out and play.

title: Nike Revolution 6
subtitle: Big Kids' Road Running Shoes
short_description: We prioritize comfort, especially for our growing athletes. Made with 20% recycled content by weight, you can take these lightweight, breathable running shoes from all-day play to anytime wear and even track practice. Lightweight, breathable and cushioned for growing feet, the race starts now.

title: Nike Air Zoom Pegasus FlyEase
subtitle: Women's Easy On/Off Road Running Shoes
short_description: Running is your daily ritual, with every step taking you closer to your personal goal. title: Nike React Infinity Run Flyknit 3
subtitle: Men's Road Running Shoes
short_description: Engineered to help you pursue your running goals in comfort, the Nike React Infinity Run Flyknit 3 remains one of our most tested shoes. Its breathable upper helps your foot feel contained but flexible. Cushioning around the heel and ankle provide a supportive and comfortable sensation mile after mile. Plus, the unique rocker-shaped sole helps allow for a smooth and stable ride on both long and short routes. So keep running, we’ve got you.

title: LeBron Witness 6
subtitle: Basketball Shoes
short_description: For this iteration of the LeBron Witness, we swapped out Zoom Air for visible Max Air cushioning—LeBron's favorite—to help dissipate impact forces and provide a responsive sensation. The lightweight, reinforced mesh upper keeps you contained all around, from the webbing that harnesses your forefoot to the external molded pieces that lock in your heel.

title: LeBron XX "Purple and Gold"
subtitle: Basketball Shoes
short_description: Serving up electrifying colors that pulse like a California sunset, the LeBron 20 takes you courtside with a look that pays tribute to the team you love. Purple Pulse and Violet Frost deliver a vibrant backdrop for game-winning Metallic Gold accents while graphics on the midsole let you settle into the LA vibe—powerful, royal and ahead of its time. Taking you into the future, the light, low-to-the-ground and ultra-cushioned design sets you up to stay on top of today’s frenzied style of play and make your mark on the next era of hoops.

title: KD15
subtitle: Basketball Shoes
short_description: Kevin Durant thrives in big games. When the stakes are high, he'll play every minute if it means getting a crucial victory. The KD15 is ready to go the distance. Lighter than his previous signature shoe, it helps you stay bouncy and comfortable in crunch time. The ride is as smooth as KD’s pull-up jumper and the cushioning is as plush as his right-to-left crossover in traffic, so that you can feel contained when your team needs you the most.

short_description: Kevin Durant thrives in big games. When the stakes are high, he'll play every minute if it means getting a crucial victory. The KD15 is ready to go the distance. Lighter than his previous signature shoe, it helps you stay bouncy and comfortable in crunch time. The ride is as smooth as KD’s pull-up jumper and the cushioning is as plush as his right-to-left crossover in traffic, so that you can feel contained when your team needs you the most.

title: LeBron 19
subtitle: Basketball Shoes
short_description: LeBron thrives when stakes are high and the pressure’s on. The LeBron 19 harnesses that energy with a locked-in fit and an updated cushioning system. The snug inner sleeve is pulled together by a sculpted overlay that the laces feed through to help prevent the foot from moving inside the shoe. Cushioned pods around the collar and tongue add comfort while reducing weight, giving players the secure feel and confidence to go all out when the game is on the line.

subtitle: Basketball Shoes

title: Nike Air Zoom G.T. Cut 2
subtitle: Basketball Shoes
short_description: You could put Devin Booker in a broom closet, and he’d find a way to create space. Ruthless jab steps. Punch dribbles at full speed. Pullback jumpers on a dime. Book is old-school footwork meets new-age flow, making him the poster boy for the G.T. Cut 2. Advanced traction helps you stop on a dime and accelerate back on command in a low-to-the-ground design that helps increase court contact while providing cushy support for all-day play.

title: Nike Renew Elevate 3
subtitle: Basketball Shoes
short_description: Level up your game on both ends of the floor in the Nike Renew Elevate 3. Specifically tuned for 2-way players who want to make an impact offensively and defensively, this shoe helps you optimize your ability with all-game, all-season support and stability. Improved traction and arch support enhance cutting and pivoting, which can make the difference down the stretch.

title: Zoom Freak 4 "Lightning"
subtitle: Basketball Shoes
short_description: Giannis is an incessant storm of stamina and skill that keeps coming at opponents for 4 quarters or more. The forward-thinking design of his latest signature shoe helps propel you down the court in a lightweight fit that moves with you. It can handle quick changes in direction on both sides of the floor, giving you side-to-side stability and multidirectional traction as you Euro step to the hoop. This special design is inspired by Giannis' electric power and speed that light up the court from night to night.

title: LeBron Witness 7
subtitle: Basketball Shoes
short_description: The longer LeBron’s legendary career continues, the more his game needs a design that doesn’t weigh him down, yet can still control all that sublime power. So, we’ve created our lightest LeBron model but with the kind of bankable support that can help you stay in front of your opponent with the game on the line. Full-length Max Air cushioning helps you take off and land confidently, while lightweight mesh blends with containment cables to help keep you locked in for 4 quarters or more.

title: LeBron Witness 6 (Team)
subtitle: Basketball Shoes
short_description: For this iteration of the LeBron Witness, we swapped out Zoom Air for visible Max Air cushioning—LeBron's favorite—to give you cushioning and provide a responsive sensation. The lightweight, reinforced mesh upper helps keep you contained all around, from the webbing that harnesses your forefoot to the external molded pieces that lock in your heel.

title: Nike Cosmic Unity 2
subtitle: Basketball Shoes
short_description: Celebrate the love and joy of the game with the Nike Cosmic Unity 2. Made with at least 20% recycled content by weight, it provides enhanced responsiveness and support. This shoe will help keep you fresh and secure without overloading it with extra ounces, so that you can focus on locking down the perimeter defensively or starting the fast break after a rebound.

title: Nike Lunar Cortez Baseball
subtitle: Baseball Cleats
short_description: City of Champions. City of Stars. We’ve turned the Lunar Cortez, a City of Angels staple, into baseball cleats, bringing the vintage sneaker to the diamond. It maintains the classic Cortez look with a little midsummer classic flair designed to inspire the next generation of players. Nods to the city’s old school charm put the finishing touches on a look made for center stage.

subtitle: Firm-Ground Soccer Cleats
short_description: Celebrate the game’s biggest competition in a design ignited by the science of connectivity and gravity that the world stage inspires. title: Nike Zoom Mercurial Vapor 15 Elite SE FG
subtitle: Firm Ground Soccer Cleats
short_description: The field is yours when you lace up in the Vapor 15 Elite FG. We added a Zoom Air unit, made specifically for soccer, and grippy texture up top for exceptional touch, so you can dominate in the waning minutes of a match—when it matters most. This special version salutes the Nike Air Zoom Mercurial VT, our 1st soccer cleat ever to sport a full-length Zoom Air unit, released in 2001. The hints of synthetic leather, copper hints and glossy finish give this game-changer a distinct retro vibe. Feel the explosive speed as you race around the field, making the critical plays with velocity and pace. Fast is in the Air.

title: Zoom Freak 4 "Kolossaio"
subtitle: Basketball Shoes
short_description: Giannis is an incessant storm of stamina and skill that keeps coming at opponents for 4 quarters or more. The forward-thinking design of his latest signature shoe helps propel you down the court in a lightweight fit that moves with you. It can handle quick changes in direction on both sides of the floor, giving you side-to-side stability and multidirectional traction as you Euro step to the hoop. This special colorway is inspired by Giannis’ gladiatorial mentality on the court and a game that will stand the test of time.

short_description: Inspired by Serena. Worn by you. Channel your inner icon in a shoe designed to celebrate the diverse perspectives of the Serena Williams Design Crew for athletes everywhere. The graphics and colors inject a shot of energy into the look, while the purple and gilded details make your feet feel majestic. Her goal in this capsule was simple—for future generations to see it and think, "I can do it too."

title: Nike Go FlyEase
subtitle: Easy On/Off Shoes
short_description: Just when you thought you'd seen it all, Nike wows with an all-new way to quickly and easily get into your shoes. Great for people with limited mobility seeking ease of entry, or anyone wanting a quicker way to get in and go! The entire heel (including the sole) of the Nike Go FlyEase pivots open for a totally hands-free entry.

title: Nike Blazer Low Platform
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: Praised for its classic simplicity and comfort, the Nike Blazer Low is your tried-and-true wardrobe staple. With its low-profile design, plush collar details and durable construction, it’s a no-brainer. We lifted the midsole to give you a fresh view of the world around you while bright, floral-inspired hues keep your style in bloom all year long. Ruffled laces add a delicate finish to this time-tested icon.

subtitle: Baby/Toddler Shoes
short_description: We went into our vault to return a late-’90s fave with the Nike Air Max Plus. subtitle: Baby Bootie

subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: In sneaker history, few styles last. Only 1 transcends every era––the Nike Air Force 1 '07 LX. Celebrate perfection with the b-ball original that delivers what you know best: woven fabric, bold details and some extra flash to keep you shining.

title: Nike Air Max Axis
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: Nodding to '90s style, the Nike Air Max Axis honors the past while looking to the future. Of course, Max Air cushions your journey.

title: Nike Air Max 90
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Lace up and feel the legacy. Produced at the intersection of art, music and culture, this champion running shoe helped define the ‘90s. Worn by presidents, revolutionized through collabs and celebrated through rare colorways, its striking visuals, Waffle outsole and exposed Air cushioning keep it alive and well.

title: Nike Air Force 1 '07 SE
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: These flower-themed AF1s invite you into the garden of good vibes. An intricate floral Swoosh design and a basket weave pattern on the upper let you kick your heels up and enjoy the day. Plus, durable leather and a classic fit give you comfort wear after wear. We think your love for this style will only grow with time.

short_description: We’ve gone into the lab to rethink everything in the Nike Air Max 2021. We put our best people on it, testing out a new Air unit with a collapsible cage that makes your feet bounce like never before. Mixing our most important features—lightweight, durable and revolutionary—we've designed these kicks with the planet in mind, too. It’s the definition of innovation for the next generation of Air Max.

title: Nike Air Max Motif Next Nature
subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
short_description: Enter a new era in Air Max history. With a futuristic take on the AM1, the Nike Air Max Motif Next Nature honors a long-standing streetwear legend. While the design lines give throwback vibes, redesigned Air units provide plush cushioning and animal print accents let you show off your wild side.

title: Nike Oneonta
subtitle: Men's Sandals
short_description: From trails to rivers to trees, these lightweight, durable sandals are ready to make adventuring fun with special thanks to their rugged tread. The Oneonta name honors the majestic falls that flow near the Columbia River in Oregon (Nike's home state). Strap in with the plush webbing system, quickly personalize your fit with an elastic cord and cinch on the heel, then get wilding.

title: Nike Star Runner 3
subtitle: Baby/Toddler Shoes
short_description: We've got some serious star power here. The Nike Star Runner 3 shoots for the sky with play-ready shoes made for each crawl to every growing step. We've added 2 straps for easy takeoff, plus supersoft foam and lots of flexibility to rocket up the comfort. Designed with the Earth in mind, they're made with at least 20% recycled content by weight.

title: Nike Air Trainer 1
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Classic fall textures meet off-court looks with the Air Trainer 1. Celebrated as one of Nike's most legendary shoes, it's gone from gym champion to wardrobe staple with adaptable looks and uncompromising comfort. Enamel Green suede overlays elevate the look and feel, while the Sail Swoosh, forefoot strap and outsole add retro appeal that's easy to style. Where will you take your Trainers?

title: Nike Air Max 90 LTR
subtitle: Big Kids’ Shoes
short_description: The Nike Air Max 90 LTR returns with an even better feel for you. Cushioning is softer and more flexible, the Max Air unit is tuned for growing feet and the shape gives your toes more wiggle room. With a design and look that are still the same, it brings a '90s fave to a new generation.

title: Nike Air Max Dawn
subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
short_description: In the Air Max world, it’s a new day with the Nike Air Max Dawn. Rooted in sporty track DNA, these kicks blend classic vintage vibes with modern details to create a look ready for the future. Simple, versatile and cushioned with Air—you can’t go wrong starting your day off in these comfy sneakers.

title: Nike ACG Lowcate
subtitle: Shoes
short_description: From streets to parks to trails, build up the miles in these city-to-adventure shoes. Designed and tested in the rugged Pacific Northwest, the mixed-material upper pairs durability with easy styling. A rubber outsole with a heavy-duty, tuned lug pattern grips slick and rocky terrain so you can go up, down, through and around.

title: Nike Blazer Mid '77
subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
short_description: Channel the old-school look of Nike basketball with the Nike Blazer Mid '77. Orange and blue add eye-catching color to a durable leather upper, helping these make a splash on the playground. Plus, a mix of throwback style and modern materials means you can run, skip and jump in comfort.

title: Nike Offline Pack
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Get ready for a sensory experience like no other—the ergonomic design, pillowy upper and comfort insole give your feet a place to relax while you get your 10,000 steps. A textile upper features soft, pillowy fabrics while the stitching details create a puffer aesthetic.

title: Nike Spark
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: Put a little spark in your step. These thoughtfully crafted kicks pair luxe comfort with extra stability—without sacrificing style. The dual foam midsole, pillowy collar and plush tongue keep you cushioned while a sleek design and textured pull tab bring energy to any 'fit.

title: Nike Air Max 90 Premium
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Nothing as fly, nothing as comfortable, nothing as proven—the Nike Air Max 90 Premium stays true to its roots with the iconic Waffle outsole, stitched overlays and classic TPU accents. Fresh colors give a modern look while Max Air cushioning adds comfort to your journey.

subtitle: Women's Shoes

title: Nike City Classic
subtitle: Women's Boots
short_description: Ready for winter matinées and cabin getaways? Get going in the City Classic Boots. Designed specifically for low-profile feet, the slim toe box and sculpted collar keep them flexible and comfortable. And because we know you've got places to be, the rugged, trail-inspired tread gives your style traction all the way to that weekend camping trip with friends.

title: Nike Court Vision Low
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: In love with the classic look of ‘80s basketball but craving casual comfort? Meet the Nike Court Vision Low. A Swoosh of blush-colored camo pops against sesame-colored leather overlays to give this old-school hoops icon an earthy update. A plush, low-cut collar keeps the design feeling sleek, modern and comfortable.

title: Nike Air VaporMax 2021 FK
subtitle: Men's Shoes

short_description: Made to keep you moving, the Nike Air VaporMax 2021 FK is airy and easy to wear with super-stretchy, Flyknit fabric (plus a soft collar that conforms to your ankle). The box stitch and confetti woven upper adds a splash of intrigue as you float down the streets on incredibly soft VaporMax cushioning.

title: Nike Flex Runner 2
subtitle: Little Kids' Shoes
short_description: Who’s ready to play? The Nike Flex Runner 2 is built for the kiddo on the go who loves to play—from the playground to wherever their day takes them. It’s laces-free! Meaning it’s super quick to slip on and off. The straps and bootie-like design make sure your little one’s fit stays snug while they run and jump.

title: Nike SB Ishod Wair
subtitle: Skate Shoes
short_description: When it came time to build his signature shoe, Ishod Wair was all-in from start to finish. Infused with elements taken from the iconic hoops shoes of the '90s, (did you know that basketball was Ishod's first love?) and built with all the durability you need to skate hard—seriously, check out that new cupsole—the Nike SB Ishod Wair walks the line between OG style and modern skate innovation.

title: Nike Air Max SC
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: With its easygoing design lines, heritage track look and visible Air cushioning, the Nike Air Max SC is the perfect finish to any outfit. A rich mixture of leather and textiles adds depth and durability. Camo-print mudguards and blush-colored Swoosh logos pop against sesame-colored leather overlays to give this everyday favorite an earthy update.

title: Nike Air Max 95 N7
subtitle: Shoes
short_description: Celebrate Native communities of North America with N7 style. Made with at least 20% recycled materials by weight, this Air Max 95's vibrantly colored, striped detailing honors the ribbon skirts worn by North American Native and Indigenous people as a symbol of self-expression, resilience and joy. Naturally dyed materials with a rich "berry stain" effect pay homage to the Indigenous defense of Mother Earth.

title: Nike Team Hustle D 10 Lil Fruits
subtitle: Baby/Toddler Shoes
short_description: Fresh, juicy colors and smoothie-inspired swirls bring a summery vibe to the Nike Team Hustle D 10 Lil Fruits, an easy slam dunk for lil’ ballers. With supersoft cushioning, an easy adjustable strap, plus a durable and supportive design, these basketball-inspired kicks let your future all-star crush it at playtime.

title: Nike Air Max 90
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: Lace up and feel the legacy. Produced at the intersection of art, music and culture, this champion running shoe helped define the ‘90s. Worn by presidents, revolutionized through collabs and celebrated through rare colorways, its striking visuals, Waffle outsole and exposed Air cushioning keep it alive and well.

subtitle: Baby/Toddler Shoes

title: Nike Crater Impact
subtitle: Women's Shoes
TopColor: Light Soft Pink/Light Silver/Arctic Orange/Smoke Grey
short_description: Nike Crater Impact is part of our sustainability journey to transform trash into shoes that tread a little lighter. Made from at least 25% recycled material by weight, it brings in unique design choices that reduces waste when compared with traditional methods––like an embroidered swoosh, efficient overlays and of course its Crater foam midsole.

subtitle: Little Kids' Shoes
short_description: The Nike Flex Advance is easy as 1, 2, 3. Nike FlyEase technology provides an extra-wide opening so little feet slip right in—seriously, it’s a piece of cake. Criss cross the straps (to help prep kiddos for real laces), and it’s done! They are super-duper flexible, comfy and durable—perfect for little ones to walk, run and play.

title: Nike Waffle One
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: Bringing a new look to the Waffle sneaker family, the Nike Waffle One balances everything you love about heritage Nike running with fresh innovations. Its new TPU heel clip adds energy while a mixture of transparent mesh (let that sock game shine) and retro suedes give texture and depth. The updated Waffle outsole provides a level of support and traction you have to feel to believe.

subtitle: Women's Slides

The iconic Air Force 1 pivot circle outsole and block lettering on the strap casually nod to heritage hoops.

title: Nike ACG Air Mada
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Slip into a shoe as ready for adventure as you are. The rugged outsole is created with a design reminiscent of climbing shoes for a classic '90s ACG look. Because we're all about the details, round laces are easy to grab with gloved hands, and materials like durable leather, sticky rubber and neoprene-like fabric help give you exactly the fit and feel you need for the mountains and beyond.

title: Nike Air Huarache
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: Built for comfort, this iteration of the Nike Air Huarache brings cool-weather-ready fabrics to a street-level favorite. Rich, textured suede on the upper mixes with super-breathable, perfectly shined neoprene-like fabric. The low-cut collar and inner sleeve keep it sleek and comfy, while the iconic heel clip and stripped-away branding keep the original '90s running look you love.

title: Nike Air Max Dawn
subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
short_description: In the Air Max world, a new day rises with the Nike Air Max Dawn. These kicks combine vintage running vibes with a special colorway inspired by the bold and expressive attitude of punk rock. Plus, the black on the Swoosh designs rubs away to reveal a vibrant new color underneath. Designed to be durable and cushioned with Air, these will have you ready to rock in no time.

title: Nike Air Max Terrascape Plus
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Recrafted in collaboration with nature, the '90s track icon turned street legend ramps up its attitude with tough, techy details. Made from at least 20% recycled materials by weight, the iconic design lets you do good by looking good. It updates your cushioning experience with the addition of our innovative Crater foam in the midsole.

title: Nike Dunk Low SE
subtitle: Little Kids' Shoes
short_description: There’s only 1 word to describe these kicks: spooktacular! While the Nike Dunk Low SE may look dark and ghostly, they’re actually the perfect sweet treat for a spooky-filled day. Suede and synthetic leather pair with a ghoulish green outsole for durable comfort and traction. But watch out—there’s something lurking in the shadows on the heel of these kicks!

subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: With its easy going lines, heritage track look and of course, visible Air cushioning, the Nike Air Max SC is the perfect finish to any outfit. The rich mixture of materials adds depth while making it a durable and lightweight shoe for everyday wear.

title: Nike Air Force 1 '07
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: The radiance lives on with the Nike Air Force 1 '07. Crossing hardwood comfort with off-court flair, this b-ball original puts a fresh spin on what you know best: era-echoing ‘80s construction, bold details and nothing-but-net style.

title: Nike Dynamo Go
subtitle: Baby/Toddler Easy On/Off Shoes
short_description: Easy, snug and built for anytime play—the Nike Dynamo Go will be your little one’s next fave. What we love most is that kiddos can stomp down on the collapsible heel and slip in quick and easy. And if they're not quite ready to do it themselves, you can show them how it works so they can be free and independent! It’s also soft and plush in the best places so the fun never stops.

subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
short_description: Everything you need for all-day play with visible Max Air? Count us in! title: Nike Air Max 90 SE
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Nothing as fly, nothing as comfortable, nothing as proven—the Nike Air Max 90 SE celebrates the 50th anniversary of the Swoosh. Staying true to its running roots with iconic Waffle sole, stitched overlays and classic TPU accents on the eyelets and heel, it now features the original Swoosh design and removable lace aglet. Other fast paced details add to the celebratory look.

title: Nike SB Shane PRM
subtitle: Skate Shoes
short_description: Shane O'Neill puts the same attention to detail into his signature shoe as he does in his almost-otherworldly skating. Now, the nearly all-white upper is ready for you to add your own personal touch. Dye, color or draw on it to tell your own story. Then lace up: its low-key ventilation, double-lacing option and no-break-in outsole keeps you ready for the streets.

title: Nike Air Rift Breathe
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: Style yourself in the perfect warm-weather look with the Nike Air Rift Breathe. Hook-and-loop strap details let you easily slide into this split-toe design based on the '96 original. Nike Air cushioning in the heel and a plush foam midsole feel softer than ever, adding that sunny beach feeling to every step.

title: Nike Little Posite One
subtitle: Little Kids' Shoes
short_description: The Nike Little Posite One reimagines 1 of our favorite basketball shoes of the '90s—for kiddos! The Foamposites were groundbreaking back in the day, and now? subtitle: Little Kids' Shoes
short_description: A color-soaked classic from high top to toe, the Chuck Taylor All Star sneaker stays forever fresh.

title: Nike Air Force 1 '07 Premium
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: A mix of real and synthetic leather, satin overlays and premium embroidery combine to celebrate the people and culture of New York City’s Ghanaian community. While embroidered backtabs honor Little Accra, a heavily Ghanaian enclave in the Bronx, metallic dubraes and graphics on the insoles encourage sharing stories and building community.

title: Nike Air Force 1 Mid '07 LX
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Crossing hardwood comfort with off-court flair, the b-ball original gets you ready for fall. Premium materials like slub canvas underlays bring a classic look, while textured leather adds sophistication to any outfit. Vintage Sail accents on the outsole and Swoosh pair with throwback labeling for a retro boost.

subtitle: Little Kids' Shoes
short_description: Made in collaboration with Space Jam: A New Legacy, the Nike Force 1 ’06 celebrates the new chapter. These legendary shoes from the hardwood get a fun reflective print that will take you out of this world.

title: Nike Air Max Goaterra 2.0
subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
short_description: Attention puddle splashers and all explorers! The Nike Air Max Goaterra 2.0 is cold-weather ready with a versatile and durable design. These boots keep it comfy with a combo of plush foam and a Max Air unit underfoot. Where will your next adventure take you?

title: Nike Manoa LTR
subtitle: Big Kids' Boots
short_description: The Nike Manoa LTR has everything you need for your next adventure: leather, soft foam cushioning and a design made to last. A rubber sole with an aggressive traction pattern helps you tackle cold, wet days.

title: Nike Dunk High Premium
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: No wardrobe is complete without aged and weathered leather. Bridging vintage style with hoops DNA, the '80s b-ball icon returns with premium leather that's been perfectly softened for a timeless look. Natural variations in the upper (don’t worry, they’re still ready for everyday wear) make it look like you've been styling them for years, while giving your kicks an elevated feel. Oh, and the plush, high-top collar lets you take your game anywhere—in comfort.

title: Nike Air Max Plus
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Every Air Max has a story. For the Air Max Plus, that story begins on a beach. A prominent arch draws inspiration from a whale’s tail, while wavy plastic overlays are a nod to palm trees blowing in the breeze. Nike Air units in the heel and forefoot create a Tuned Air experience that offers incredible stability and unbelievable cushioning. Lace them up and step into defiant style.

title: Nike Waffle One Crater
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Eye candy for your feet. Bringing classic track style into the modern realm with at least 20% recycled materials by weight, these kicks let you do good by looking good. The wedge midsole is made from supportive foam. The sporty, era-echoing design adds throwback to your step. And for added dimension, the iconic Waffle outsole is speckled with the bold colors of Nike Grind.

subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: A flash from the past, the Nike Court Royale 2 Mid features the perfect banana-shaped sole that rocked the streets in the late '70s. Leather on the upper looks crisp, feels smooth and is easy to wear.

title: Nike Huarache Run
subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
short_description: Stay balanced as you play in these inspired kicks. With its unmistakable heel strap—grab it and slide your foot right into the snug inner sleeve—the Nike Huarache Run is all about secure comfort. Subtle yin-yang symbols decorate the insoles and sidewall, encouraging you to seek harmony in your day.

title: Nike Lunar Force 1
subtitle: Men's Duckboot
short_description: When it's colder than the far side of the moon and spitting rain too, you still got to look good. From water-repellent leather to a rugged outsole, the Lunar Force 1 adapts AF1 style so you can keep your flame burning when the weather hits. Metal lace hardware and extended tongue bring mountain boot toughness, while the star studded toe design gives your look the edge.

title: Nike Space Hippie 01
subtitle: Shoes
short_description: Space Hippie is a story of trash transformed. Combining its airy Space Waste Yarn upper with its ultra-soft Crater foam midsole, the Space Hippie 01 delivers a futuristic look that feels as light as mountain air. The sleek, track-inspired silhouette also features a vibrant Swoosh design and unique lacing system that minimize the production process. Made from at least 50% recycled materials, it lets you lace up, salvage your world and live your dreams.

short_description: The Nike Flex Advance for lil’ kiddos are easy as 1, 2, 3. Nike FlyEase technology provides an extra-wide opening so little feet slip right in (seriously, it’s a piece of cake). Attach the 2-piece strap across the top, and it's done! They're super-duper flexible, comfy and durable—perfect for little one to grow from crawling to their first steps.

title: Nike Victori One
subtitle: Men's Shower Slides
short_description: You've played hard. You've sweated. You've given your all. Now there's just one last thing—you have to hit the showers. Don't worry, we got your back with the Nike Victori One. Its 1-piece foam design feels soft and comfortable while traction patterns on the sole help with wet surfaces. They dry quickly too, so no one will know you've just stepped from the showers as you slide up to the party.

title: Nike Burrow SE
subtitle: Men's Slippers
short_description: There's nothing like cozying up to a campfire, which is why we made these extra toasty and super comfortable slippers. A mix of knit and fleece-like materials deliver the perfect wintertime warmth and fireside feel. And the marshmallow soft foam midsole and outsole sweeten the deal. Slip them on and get lounging or step out of the tent and enjoy the fresh mountain air.

title: Nike BRSB
subtitle: Skate Shoes
short_description: A familiar favorite is reborn in the Nike BRSB. Almost every detail, from the color blocking to the sawtooth pattern on the sole, was inspired by the original Nike Cortez. But, because this shoe is built for skate, we added extras where they're needed—like the rubber from the sole that wraps up and over the heel and toe for durability. It also wraps the sides, adding an extra layer to high-use areas, like the ollie zone.

title: Nike Air Force 1 Crater
subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
short_description: The radiance lives on in the Nike Air Force 1 Crater. A transparent Swoosh design reveals a swoop of color underneath for a fun, painted effect. Air units in the heels and soft foam underfoot help make every step you take feel cushioned and comfortable.

title: Nike ACG Mountain Fly Low SE
subtitle: Shoes
short_description: Fast, rugged and just as at home in the city as it is on rocky trails, the Nike ACG Mountain Fly Low SE arrives in an updated, low-profile silhouette with a lightweight upper. title: Nike Air Force 1 '07 Premium
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: A mix of real and synthetic leather, satin overlays and premium embroidery come together in this anniversary edition of the Nike Air Force 1 ’07 Premium to celebrate the people and culture of New York City’s Ghanaian community. While embroidered backtabs honor Little Accra, a heavily Ghanaian enclave in the Bronx, graphics on the insoles and metallic dubraes with adinkra symbols encourage sharing stories and building community.

short_description: There’s only 1 word to describe these kicks: Spooktacular! While the Nike Dunk Low SE may look dark and ghostly, they’re actually a super sweet treat for a spooky-filled day. Suede and synthetic leather pair with a ghoulish green outsole for durable comfort and traction. But watch out—there’s something lurking in the shadows on the heels of these kicks!

title: Nike Air More Uptempo '96
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Bold, eye-catching and all about the A-I-R. The Nike Air More Uptempo '96 refreshes an original that has reigned supreme for more than 20 years. With a design inspired by high-flying basketball style and '90s graffiti art, these kicks can't help but turn heads off court. Plus, Air units in the heel, forefoot and midfoot provide comfortable cushioning so you feel as good as you look.

subtitle: Little Kids' Shoes
short_description: Fresh, juicy colors and smoothie-inspired swirls bring a summery vibe to the Nike Team Hustle D 10 Lil Fruits, an easy slam dunk for future players. With a traction pattern tailored for little ones, soft cushioning and a design that’s durable and supportive, these basketball-inspired shoes let your future all-star crush it at playtime.

title: Nike Dunk Low Disrupt 2
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: Make every outfit an opportunity for self-expression. Amplifying a hoops icon, these superfly, customizable sneakers go beyond the tried and true. Multiple lace-up options and an extra set of laces let you personalize your look to match the day.

title: Nike Waffle Racer Crater
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: From scraps to the streets, we put a fresh twist on the 1977 OG. The Nike Waffle Racer Crater combines Crater Foam with Nike Grind rubber details for a rugged, track-inspired look, weighing in with at least 20% recycled materials. The Crater Foam midsole is made from a spacey mix of foam materials and 10% Nike Grind rubber, while the speckled Waffle outsole is made from 15% Nike Grind rubber, making each pair unique and durable.

title: Nike Oneonta Be True
subtitle: Sandals
short_description: Reinvent what it means to be you. Celebrating the LGBTQIA+ community, these lightweight, durable sandals are ready for your next adventure. Gradient branding and colorful straps pair with paint-speckled, rugged tread and plush cushioning so you can go from streets to trails without pause.

title: Nike Blazer Mid '77 Premium
subtitle: Men's Basketball Shoes
short_description: Maybe you're the king of microbrews and vintage rock. Maybe you just really like suede. Either way, the Blazer Mid '77 offers a soft, worn-in look with just the right amount of old-school feel. Soft suede brings instant comfort while the retro Swoosh brings a retro finish.

title: Nike Air Max 90 SE
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: The heirloom of style—the Nike Air Max 90 SE stays true to its roots with its iconic Waffle outsole, stitched overlays and classic plastic accents. The metallic upper and shoewelry dubrae bring a triumphant look to your outfit.

title: Nike Little Posite One
subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
short_description: Time to freestyle! The Nike Little Posite One is inspired by mixtapes from generations of the past and today. Iridescent accents and hidden details for you to find celebrate the technological evolution of mixtapes—from music to sports. The colorful design meets a ‘90s hoops original for an awesome remix.

subtitle: Shoes

title: Nike Retro GTS
subtitle: Men's Shoe
short_description: There's no need for frills when you're classic. The Nike Retro GTS is just that—a classically simple, always stylish canvas shoe. Nodding to the '96 original that gave a generation of skaters their don't-care attitude, the new design gets updated with a comfort insole, embroidered logos and metal eyelets. Featuring a canvas upper and tough rubber sole with heritage herringbone traction pattern it lets you turn heads without trying.

short_description: These everyday kicks throw it back by mashing up details from ‘80s running shoes. Plus, did you know? The Nike MD Valiant is full of history. They're named after the car that Nike's co-founder sold shoes out of during the early days—the '64 Valiant.

title: Nike Max 90 Crib SE
subtitle: Baby Booties
short_description: What we love: animal prints. Paw prints. Follow the trail left by your little critter when they rock the Nike Max 90 Crib SE. What we love even more: The soft, cozy fur-like details that bring these to life. Let your kiddo imagine themselves as their favorite animal when they go out and play. Our only question is: which animal is that?

title: Nike Cortez Basic SL
subtitle: Little Kids' Shoe
short_description: Originally made for the track, the Nike Cortez Basic SL has become a streetwear icon. These classic kicks (that debuted in ’72) keep the same OG design lines, and are made super durable and cushioned underfoot. Plus, we make it easy for kiddos with 2 straps so playtime never waits.

title: Nike Space Hippie 04
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: Space Hippie is a story of trash transformed. From the upper to the outsole, Space Hippie 04 is made of at least 25% recycled material by weight. Not only is it the most lightweight silhouette within the collection, its ‘Space Waste Yarn’ upper includes recycled content—made from recycled plastic bottles, t-shirts and yarn scraps—for a lower carbon footprint. A soft, Crater Foam midsole combines Nike grind with a blend of foams for stability and a unique aesthetic.

title: Nike SB BLZR Court Mid Premium
subtitle: Skate Shoes
short_description: We took the classic styling of the Nike SB BLZR Court Mid Premium and gave it a workwear twist. It still has the same, lightweight, flexible feel as the original but we added a paisley print to the lining and chain-stitched "Nike" onto the heel. The result is a sleek, skate-ready silhouette with an understated, slightly rugged vibe.

title: Nike Air Force 1 '07 Next Nature
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: The radiance lives on in the Nike Air Force 1 '07 Next Nature. Made with strong and durable woven poly hemp, these b-ball icons get updated with a few pops of bright colors. Of course, you still get Nike Air cushioning and the iconic pivot-circle outsole that helped make the ’82 original famous. Plus, the speckled outsole uses Nike Grind—rubber containing at least 13% recycled content.

title: Nike Air Max TW
subtitle: Little Kids' Shoes
short_description: What does your kiddo notice first about the Nike Air Max TW? The cool bubbles or Air they can feel with every step? The sweet boomerang design on the sides? Or the lightweight and breathable feel inspired by the iconic Tailwind running shoes of the past? They may notice it all, but either way, this will be their next favorite pair of kicks.

subtitle: Women's Sandals
short_description: Summertime is a feeling and the Nike Owaysis is summertime at its best—simple, comfortable and versatile. title: Nike Burrow
subtitle: Women's Slipper
TopColor: Arctic Orange/Light Soft Pink/Orange Frost/Pink Oxford
short_description: There's nothing like cozying up to a campfire. Nothing like adventure. But also, there's nothing like the comfort of home. The Nike Burrow lets you bridge worlds. Slip them on and get lounging or step out of the tent and enjoy the fresh mountain air. Its fleece-like lining helps keep you warm. The marshmallow soft foam midsole/outsole with grippy traction pattern adds spring to your step.

subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes

title: Nike Air Force 1 Sage Low
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: Taking height and craft to new levels, the Nike Air Force 1 Sage Low reimagines classic hoops style—by and for women. A clean leather upper is easy to style. The sculpted collar reduces hot spots. And its platform midsole adds unflinching boldness because we know: you’re not just in the game, you're leading it.

title: Nike Spark Flyknit
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: We're anti fatigue and pro play, which is why we created the Nike Spark Flyknit. Utilizing a layered midsole (firm foam, plastic plate and soft foam), it reduces flection in the forefoot to help keep you energized. The visually stunning, dual-layer Flyknit upper is airy, supportive and easy to style, while the carved-away design lets you see the tech that keeps you comfortable. So if anyone dares you to keep going, lace-up and accept.

title: Nike Air Vapormax 2020 FlyKnit
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Designed with sustainability in mind, the Nike Air VaporMax 2020 Flyknit is made from at least 50% recycled content by weight. That’s a lot of trash! As part of Nike’s journey towards lowering our impact, we’re discovering new ways to put our waste to good use. By utilizing leftover materials, recycled polyester, recycled foam, and a Nike Air sole made from at least 75% recycled TPU, the VaporMax 2020 Flyknit marks the next step towards our ultimate goal of zero carbon and zero waste.

subtitle: Men's Boots

short_description: Bring off-court details and rugged looks into a new realm. title: Nike Air Force 1 Mid '07 LX
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: The '84 Low. The '93 Mid. The '07 Re-issue. A lot happens in 40 years. We’ve run the numbers and tallied up iconic moments in AF1 history to put the ultimate receipt in your hands. The removable timeline on this anniversary edition chronicles each coveted drop, while embroidered accents and playful graphics nod to the genesis of the hoops original. A combination of premium leather, canvas and cork make for a truly commemorative look. Whether these are your first pair or just the latest in your collection, we’ve got you covered with legendary style straight out of the box.

title: Nike Air Max TW
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: So you're in love with the classic look of the '90s, but you got a thing for today's fast-paced culture. Meet the Air Max TW. Inspired by the treasured franchise that brought Nike Air cushioning to the world and laid the foundation for the track-to-street aesthetic, its eye-catching design delivers a 1-2 punch of comfort and fashion. Ready to highlight any ‘fit, its lightweight upper pairs angular and organic lines to create an entrancing haptic effect. The contrasting colorways make it easy to style. And if you’re ready for the next step, the 5 windows underfoot deliver a modern edge to visible Air cushioning.

subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Meet the leader of the pack. First released in 1987, the Nike Air Max 1 was the first shoe in the family to bring Air to the world. With a fast-paced look, tried-and-true cushioning and classic wavy mudguard, it’s no wonder it’s reigned supreme ever since.

title: Nike Air Force 1 '07 Premium
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Step into never-ending style with the Air Force 1 '07 Premium. Inspired by LA’s open-air flea markets, it brings the heat with an old-meets-new aesthetic. Mixed and matched materials pair with exaggerated stitching and frayed details to create a crafty DIY look that honors the streetwear mecca’s flair for pushing boundaries and breathing new life into hand-me-downs. For extra sunny vibes, we embroidered California poppies throughout.

title: Nike LeBron IX
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: It’s been ten years since the LeBron 9 made its debut and helped propel King James to a championship. Now, the model is back in its original form, making it ready for pickup games and hitting the streets afterwards. This new “South Coast” makeup features familiar neon hues and palm tree graphics—paying homage to where LeBron’s taken his basketball roots throughout his career. Special insoles with King James custom graphics add a royal touch every time you lace-up.

short_description: Summer showers don’t have to put a damper on your day, or your look. Durable synthetic leather, semi-transparent molded overlays and a padded, high-cut collar with hook-and-loop closure adds heritage b-ball comfort to make these feel as good as they look.

title: Nike ISPA Link
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Don't get puzzled. Zero glue, two pieces and a whole lot of comfort. Constructed with interlocking components, the ISPA Link was designed for disassembly and with the intent to use as few materials as possible. Spotlighting comfort, it places you directly on top of an ultrasoft foam midsole. The engineered knit upper keeps it airy and lightweight, while the bootie-like fit gives your foot a hug with every step. Get going, keep going—it's as easy as 1, 2.

title: Nike Dynamo Go
subtitle: Little Kids' Easy On/Off Shoes
short_description: Easy, snug and built for anytime play—the Nike Dynamo Go will be your little one’s next fave. title: Nike Air Force 1 '07 LV8
subtitle: Men's Shoes

subtitle: Women's Shoes

Finishing it off, the Waffle-inspired outsole adds true Nike zest.

subtitle: Little Kids' Shoes
short_description: Follow the trail of pawprints left by your little critter when they rock the Nike Air Max 90 Toggle. Slip them on, adjust the toggle and let your kiddo imagine themselves as their favorite animal.

subtitle: Women's Shoes

subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: Take your love for the game with you wherever you go. Of course, we kept the same era-echoing '80s construction and hidden Air units you know and love for that legendary AF1 feel. Go ahead, slip into a slam dunk.

title: Nike Waffle One SE
subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
short_description: The Nike Waffle One pays tribute to an early innovation that helped launch us toward success: the Waffle outsole. Back in Nike’s early days, founder Bill Bowerman used a waffle iron to create a studded outsole with traction that was perfect for runners. Now, that same pattern brings you traction ideal for all-day play. Plus, we made these durable so you can wear them over and over again. They’re ready for whatever adventures you have planned!

title: Nike Air Force 1 Premium
