title: Nike Space Hippie 04
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: Space Hippie is a story of trash transformed. From the upper to the outsole, Space Hippie 04 is made of at least 25% recycled material by weight. Not only is it the most lightweight silhouette within the collection, it also has the lowest carbon footprint. Its ‘Space Waste Yarn’ upper includes about 75% recycled content by weight–made from recycled plastic bottles, t-shirts and yarn scraps. A soft, Crater Foam midsole combines Nike grind with a blend of foams for stability and a unique aesthetic.

title: Nike Air Force 1 Crater
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: We remixed a classic with at least 20% recycled material by weight, making the Air Force 1 Crater a sneaker for the modern era. The translucent toe reveals a vibrant blend of materials beneath for a bold, 1-of-a-kind look. Nike Grind rubber on the outsole keeps the iconic star pattern on the tip while the unique speckle of the Crater Foam midsole brings the OG into the future.

title: Nike Little Posite One
subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
short_description: The Nike Little Posite One reimagines 1 of our favorite basketball shoes of the '90s—for kids! The Foamposites were groundbreaking back in the day, and now? They're a streetwear icon. These durable and supportive kicks let you feel confident for class, recess and on your way home after a full day of fun.

title: Nike Dunk Low
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: Created for the hardwood but taken to the streets, the Dunk is back. This ‘80s hoops icon returns with crisp leather overlays and plenty of b-ball flair. It channels vintage style with its classic design. A padded, low-cut collar lets you comfortably take your game anywhere.

title: Nike Blazer Mid '77 Jumbo
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Praised by many for its enduring look and feel, the wardrobe staple hits refresh with the Nike Blazer Mid '77 Jumbo. Harnessing the old-school look you love, it now has an elastic heel with corduroy-like texture and large pull tabs for easy on and off. The oversized Swoosh design and jumbo laces add a fun twist.

short_description: Fun fact: The Nike Cortez was the first track shoe released by Nike back in '72. Designed by cofounder Bill Bowerman, it's become a sneaker legend today. This classic look is made kid-right with 2 straps so playtime never waits.

Plus, the durable heel clip and leather upper add to the classic look.

short_description: Comfy, flexible and super easy to wear—the Nike Free Run 2 transforms a running shoe into all-day kicks. The deep grooves in the sole are the signature of the Free’s “barefoot-like” feel. With soft foam underfoot and a secure strap, kiddos can count on these versatile low-tops from class to playtime and everywhere in between.

title: Nike Air Max 97
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Like the Japanese bullet trains that inspired their iconic ripple design, these kicks go full speed ahead. Sleek, stylish, and revolutionary, they're dressed in an all-black color scheme and cushioned with the full-length Nike Air unit that shook up the running world in '97. In short: this is a first-class ride you don't want to miss.

short_description: With its effortless transition from hardwood to off-court dominance, the Nike Air Total Max Uptempo brings you a near 1-to-1 remake of the innovative original that has reigned supreme for 20 years. The rippled side panel features exposed needlework and textured leather while embroidered accents add to the richness. Its chrome heel plate completes the look while full-length Max Air cushioning delivers performance comfort.

title: Nike Dunk Low

title: Nike Manoa Leather SE
subtitle: Men's Boots
short_description: Durable leather, breathable textile and rugged lugs combine to create the Nike Manoa Boot—your perfect city-to-trail boot. Heavy-duty details include a webbing pull tab, hexagonal metal eyelets and a durable rubber outsole. The padded, mid-height collar is easy to style and feels great.

short_description: They say the way to the heart is through chocolate. They're wrong. Lace into true bliss with this crafted take on the b-ball original. The leather tongue label and dubrae add an artisan touch while Air cushioning puts the cherry on the bottom—setting you softly on cloud 9.

title: Nike Air Max 97 Premium

The original look, inspired by Japanese bullet trains and water droplets, still takes center stage, while easy-to-style colors let you hit the streets quickly. Full-length Nike Air cushioning lets you ride in first-class comfort.

Exposed foam on the tongue and a special midsole finish make it seem as if you've just pulled them from the history books. Go ahead, perfect your outfit.

Made from at least 20% recycled materials by weight.

short_description: The Nike AF1s are a legend for a reason. From the basketball courts in the '80s to the streets (and schools) today, they've been a sneaker icon everywhere for decades—meaning a long time! Expect extra durability and cushioning without added bulk—the fly-as-ever silhouette looks just as good on the hiking trail as it does on the sidewalk.

short_description: The radiance lives on with the b-ball original. Celebrating 50 years of Nike innovation, it lets you step back in time with '70s-styled graphics and vintage colors. Let peace, love and sport bring you nothin’-but-net style.

title: Nike Air Max Goaterra 2.0
subtitle: Men's Boots
short_description: Keep it rugged in the Nike Air Max Goaterra 2.0. Constructed with perfectly shined premium leather, it's got a finish that's designed to help you stay dry. Sturdy and street-ready, this boot can be dressed up or dressed down depending on the mood. The ultra-padded collar and Air cushioning in the heel make it comfortable.

title: Nike Air Force 1 '07 LV8
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Crossing hardwood comfort with off-court flair, the Nike Air Force 1 '07 LV8 adds a touch of crafty style to a hoops original with cozy textures and bold patterns. Soft textile fabrics bring a new look and feel to the AF1 franchise while hidden Air units keep the comfortable cushioning you love. Plus, fun stitched details and metallic gold dubraes add a sense of playfulness to chilly nights.

title: Nike Canyon
subtitle: Men's Sandals
short_description: Your journey starts with the Nike Canyon Sandal. This rugged hiker is ready to explore. The ACG-inspired design features a beefy outsole, plush foam midsole, and triple-strap closure. From cityscapes to the river banks, this versatile powerhouse will keep you steady on your feet and comfortable tackling whatever lies ahead. Enjoy your time away. You’ve earned it.

title: Nike Air Max Motif
subtitle: Little Kids' Shoes
short_description: Enter a new era in Air Max history. The Nike Air Max Motif honors the iconic AM1—a streetwear legend since ‘87—with a futuristic take for your kiddo’s generation. The design lines give throwback vibes and a redesigned Air unit has supersoft cushioning, so little feet have everything they need for all-day play.

title: Nike Air Max Motif
subtitle: Little Kids' Shoes
short_description: Enter a new era in Air Max history. The Nike Air Max Motif honors the iconic AM1—a streetwear legend since ‘87—with a futuristic take for your kiddo’s generation. The design lines give throwback vibes and a redesigned Air unit has supersoft cushioning, so little feet have everything they need for all-day play.

title: Nike Air Max 90 SE
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Celebrate your passion for the pitch in this soccer-inspired design. While keeping the classic aesthetic of the Air Max 90, we've added a digital print and crowned ball logo—giving you Anywhere FC attitude.

title: Nike LeBron 9 Low
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: With its vibrant, tropical theme, this LeBron brings a fresh twist to the classic, thirst-quenching combination of iced tea and lemonade. Celebrating the famed refreshment, it mixes fresh colors, airy materials and lavish ornamental graphics fit for a king. Drink it up with your eyes while you give your feet a vacation.

title: Nike Air Force 1 High '07 LV8 Vintage
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: The Nike Air Force 1 High '07 LV8 Vintage is everything you know best: crisp leather overlays, bold accents and classic hoops style. The padded, high-cut collar with hook-and-loop closure adds heritage b-ball comfort while the rubber outsole gives your look traction on and off the court.

title: Nike Air Max Dia Winter
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: Designed specifically for a woman's foot, the Nike Air Max Dia Winter delivers a lifted and airy aesthetic in a sleek shape. The minimal upper modernizes the look, while a Max Air unit is amplified even further by an exaggerated midsole for a boost of style.

title: Nike Air Max Dia Winter
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: Designed specifically for a woman's foot, the Nike Air Max Dia Winter delivers a lifted and airy aesthetic in a sleek shape. The minimal upper modernizes the look, while a Max Air unit is amplified even further by an exaggerated midsole for a boost of style.

title: Nike Air Force 1 '07 Fresh
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: You can’t stop aging, but the Air Force 1 "Fresh" gets pretty close. Soft, textured leather helps conceal creasing and is easy to clean. The debossed branding, which replaces the woven labels, pairs with extra laces so you can eat that jelly doughnut in peace. And the perforated sockliner keeps it airy and breathable. Now, there's really no reason not to rock white-on-white.

title: Nike Air Max 90 x LHM
subtitle: Shoes
short_description: Each shoe in the Familia collection is a celebration of Latin America's iconic heritage in sport. The expressive colors and patterns are inspired by the culture, energy and raw authenticity, all driven by a deep love of family. This shoe is a walking symbol—a vibrant representation of a legacy that precedes sport and a future that will be defined by it.

title: Nike Air Force 1 LV8
subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
short_description: These Nike AF1s are your NEWWW world champion! Celebrate with these classic kicks inspired by the theater of pro wrestling. Sport the gold details like you're best in the world. Rock the edgy look with cracked durable leather. Made for everyday wear, feel like a champ from the opening bell to your finishing move.

title: Nike WearAllDay SE
subtitle: Baby/Toddler Shoes
short_description: The Nike WearAllDay SE is simple: Everyday kicks that are versatile, durable and comfy enough for anything. Check out the details of this edition that are inspired by award medals to celebrate your future winner.

title: Nike Tanjun
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: "Tanjun" means "simplicity" in Japanese, and the Nike Tanjun is elegant simplicity at its best. It has a modern design that is convenient and comfortable, with a sleek upper that gives a clean look.

title: Nike Challenger OG
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Nearly a 1-to-1 remake of the OG running shoe that offered runners a distinct look in the '70s, the Nike Challenger OG marries soft suedes, shimmering fabric and breathable mesh. Plush padding around the ankle combines with its sleek, springy midsole to make it the comfy trendsetter—the diamond from underground.

title: Nike Air Max 95
subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
short_description: The Nike Air Max 95 is back with fast-paced style that’s perfect for the playground. Vibrant, high-energy colors add a fun twist to this iconic sneaker while Max Air in the forefoot and heel help cushion your every hop, skip and jump.

title: Nike Court Borough Mid
subtitle: Little Kids' Shoes
short_description: Littles can feel like all-stars off the court with the Nike Court Borough Mid. The mid-tops’ design and feel are inspired by the iconic AF1 for throwback hoops style. Made with durable leather and an easy strap for extra support, they’re built to last and look fresh no matter what.

title: Nike Air Force 1 '07 Premium
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: A legend in two games. This Air Force 1 pays tribute to hip-hop's Bronx Origins and the 40th anniversary of the sneaker icon. Since it arrived in '82, the AF1 has been intrinsically tied to the world's most influential music genre, serving as the uniform sneaker for the culture. The dubraes dawn two key years—1973 and 1982—highlighting the birthdates of hip-hop & the inception of AF1 as we know it. And to top it off, the Swoosh & wide laces are reminiscent of a time when the scratch of a record brought people together & the thickness of your laces defined "cool."

title: Nike Air Max Excee
subtitle: Big Kids’ Shoes
short_description: The Nike Air Max Excee honors 30+ years since the release of the iconic Air Max 90. Inspired by the original design, these low-top kicks add a crafty look and a mix of textures for a new twist on a ‘90s favorite. FYI, Excee means 90 in Latin.

title: Nike Air Max Excee
subtitle: Big Kids’ Shoes

title: Nike Force 1 '06 LV8 EMB
subtitle: Little Kids' Shoes
short_description: The Nike Force 1 ’06 LV8 EMB reimagines a hoops icon into legendary streetwear kicks for kiddos. These classics get elevated with a mix of leather and satin for a basketball-like feel. Show the world that ball is life.

What are you waiting for, get lounging.

subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
short_description: There's a lot to love about the AF1: Its tough stitching and grippy tread help you find your footing on first days and rainy days alike. It's the shoe that was as cool 20 years ago as it is today, and will be even when it's covered in stains, scuffs and scrapes from days of play. Actually, you might love it even more!

short_description: The Nike Air Max 270 React mashes up artistic style with nonstop cushioning. The colors and textures honor art movements over the last 100+ years. Classic Max Air also has our innovative React foam for a super bouncy ride all day, any day.

short_description: Imagine a shoe you didn't have to tie but could just step in and go. The Nike Glide FlyEase makes your dreams a reality with a FlyEase design that lets you get into your shoes with little effort. short_description: Designed to feel as comfy as a favorite tee, the Nike Presto Extreme Infant/Toddler Shoe offers distinctive, adaptive style and great flexibility.

subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: So you're in love with the classic look of '80s basketball, but you've got a thing for the fast-paced culture of today's game. Meet the Nike Court Vision Low. Its crisp, textured upper and stitched overlays are inspired by the hook-shot look of old-school b-ball while its super-plush, low-cut collar keeps it sleek and comfortable day in and day out.

title: Nike Dunk High
subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
short_description: Take your day sky high in this hoops legend. The Nike Dunk returns with durability and support for every baller. With vintage vibes and sized for kids, this is an easy slam dunk for your kicks collection.

subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Move over milk, the power of the Air Max 95 is in town, and it's got style you'll feel all the way to your bones. Taking inspiration from the human body and '90s track aesthetics, it taps into "The Anatomy of Air" with a skeletal-inspired colorway and midsole print representing the inside of a bone. Premium suede, glow-in-the-dark details and a surprise on the bottom finish it off.

subtitle: Women's Shoes

The sporty design includes hits of iconic branding, a super-soft foam midsole/outsole with flex grooves and a unique slip-on design that's been perfected for ease of entry. The simple color schemes make it easy to style so you can focus on everything else.

subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: The Nike Air VaporMax EVO puts Air Max DNA under the microscope to showcase the distinguishing features of 7 Nike icons. From stitched overlays, to classic accents to unbelievable comfort and overt '90s styling, it splices the must-haves of your favorite Air Max shoes onto 1 new design. Evolve your look and feel the comfort of everything Max.

title: Nike Flow 2020 ISPA
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: The Nike Flow 2020 ISPA puts forth a sophisticated solution to complex footwear problems. The unique pull-string lacing system lets you easily customize your fit on the go while strategically placed mesh provides ventilation where you need it. Transluscent rubber accents add toughness and textile on the upper creates a sock-like feel that stands up to wear.

title: Nike ACG GORE-TEX "Mountain Fly"
subtitle: Shoes
short_description: Fast, rugged and just as at home in the city as it is rocky trails, the Nike ACG GORE-TEX "Mountain Fly" is ready for whatever you throw at it. The lightweight upper uses GORE-TEX technology to help keep the weather out and has a gator for on-the-go personalization. The sticky rubber outsole brings crag-inspired traction. And because we know it'll take you everywhere, we've paired plush Nike React foam with Vaporfly technology for undisputed comfort.

title: Nike Air Max 90 Toggle SE
subtitle: Baby/Toddler Shoes
short_description: Follow the trail of pawprints left by your little critter when they rock the Nike Air Max 90 Toggle. Furry Swoosh logos bring these shoes to life while a toggle system helps secure the fit. An Air unit in the heel provides comfortable cushioning so little ones are ready to play. Slip them on, adjust the toggle and let your kiddo imagine themselves as their favorite animal.

title: Nike Air Max 90 SE
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Strap a little sunshine to your feet with the Nike Air Max 90 SE. Carefree details and fresh colors deliver a beach day forecast. Airy, summertime fabrics are made from at least 20% recycled materials by weight and keep the classic 90 aesthetic you know best: iconic Waffle sole, durable accents and visible Air cushioning.

title: Nike Kepa Kai
subtitle: Men's Slides
short_description: The Nike Kepa Kai Slide delivers the underfoot comfort of dual-density foam in a casual thong, ideal for all-day wear in warm weather. Soft, lined straps provide a secure fit, while the herringbone texture on the footbed and outsole add grip instead of slip.

title: Nike Force 1 LV8
subtitle: Baby/Toddler Shoe
short_description: The Nike Force 1 LV8 is plant-tastic! We’ve reimagined the ’82 legend with at least 20% recycled content, including canvas with cork accents. Still durable and cushioned, is your little one ready to plant these kicks on their feet?

title: Nike Air Max 90
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Nothing as fly, nothing as comfortable, nothing as proven—the Nike Air Max 90 stays true to its OG roots. Bold heritage colors, an iconic Waffle sole and classic TPU accents on the heel and eyestays keep the '90s look you love. Max Air cushioning adds comfort to your journey. This edition brings back a hyper royal upper coupled with bright crimson details and milk-toned accents to make you look as sweet as they feel.

title: Nike Air Force 1 Low Retro QS
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Can an icon get more iconic? This AF1 goes for it with an anniversary edition of the 2002 design honoring the cultures of the West Indies. Crisp white is punctuated with pops of color throughout, and features an embroidered "West Indies" and palm tree. Take a peek at the insole for your very own geography lesson, just in time for the annual parade in Brooklyn that celebrates the islands.

title: Nike Downshifter 11
subtitle: Baby/Toddler Shoe
short_description: 3, 2, 1, GO! The Nike Downshifter 11 sets the pace for lil' kiddos with lightweight comfort for play and adventures. They’re breathable, cushioned and durable where little feet need it. Plus, they easily adjust with a strap! The only question is: how long can playtime last?

title: Nike Air Force 1 Mid '07

short_description: The Air Force 1 Mid '07 is everything you know best: crisp overlays, fresh accents, and the perfect details to let your shoe game shine. The padded, mid-height collar with classic hook-and-loop closure adds heritage b-ball comfort. Nike Air cushioning in the heel delivers performance comfort.

Vibrant hues boost the energy, while soft suede and canvas elevate the look and feel of your 'fit. In our memories, in our hearts, for a lifetime and beyond…Somos Familia.

The wavy side panels add water-like flow, while visible Nike Air cushioning delivers performance comfort. Go ahead and take your chance.

short_description: Show some love to big Air. The Nike Air Max Bolt is all about the huge Air-Sole unit that’s hard to miss. Plus, these everyday kicks are supportive and cushy to help you feel confident while you play.

Plus, an iconic Waffle outsole and Max Air unit adds durable traction and comfortable cushioning that's perfect for playtime. Lace them up and create magical moments with your mini.

title: Nike Force 1 LV8 2
subtitle: Baby/Toddler Shoes
short_description: Start your little one’s sneaker collection with the legendary AF1. With their smooth leather, durable rubber sole and unmistakable Swoosh design, they’ve been an icon for a long, long time (since the ‘80s). This edition got a retro refresh inspired by our own history with ‘70s-style graphics on the tongue, heel and laces. So groovy!

title: Nike Air Force 1 Premium
subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
short_description: Crossing hardwood comfort with off-court flare, this b-ball original continues to stand the test of time, generation after generation. Clean lines, bold details and nothin’-but-net-style make these classic, court-inspired sneakers the perfect streetwear staple for anyone and everyone.

title: Nike Star Runner 3 SE
subtitle: Baby/Toddler Shoes
short_description: Made for future runners + gamers alike, the Nike Star Runner 3 SE brings some serious star power. From the digitized Swoosh to pixelated graphics, we bring the world of video games to life. These lightweight shoes have 2 straps for easy on and off, and plush foam under little feet to level up the comfort for playtime.

title: Nike Air Force 1 LV8
subtitle: Big Kid's Shoes
short_description: The radiance lives on in the Nike Air Force 1 LV8. Crossing hardwood comfort with off-court flair, these kicks put a fresh spin on 1 of our most legendary sneakers. Bright retro-inspired graphics on the tongue celebrate ‘90s heritage while hidden Air units and a padded collar help keep playtime comfy. And of course, you still get the crisp leather, bold colors and nothing-but-net style our AF1s are known for.

title: Nike Force 1 LV8 2
subtitle: Little Kids' Shoes
short_description: The Nike AF1s are legendary. With their smooth leather, durable rubber sole and unmistakable Swoosh design, they’ve been a sneaker icon for decades. That’s a long time! We gave this special edition a retro refresh with ‘70s-style graphics on the tongue, heel and laces. They're a groovy blast from the past!

title: Nike Force 1 LV8 3
subtitle: Baby/Toddler Shoes
short_description: The Nike Force 1 LV8 3 refreshes the icon from 1982 with soft suede leather. Foam cushioning helps keep little feet comfy for all-day play.

title: Nike Air Max Axis
subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
short_description: A nod to '90s running, the Nike Air Max Axis honors the past while looking ahead to the future. Subtle design lines and branding pay homage to icons like the Air Max 97 and Air Max 98, while a new look at the Air-Sole unit offers a fresh take on cushioned comfort.

title: Nike Air Max Axis
subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
short_description: A nod to '90s running, the Nike Air Max Axis honors the past while looking ahead to the future. Subtle design lines and branding pay homage to icons like the Air Max 97 and Air Max 98, while a new look at the Air-Sole unit offers a fresh take on cushioned comfort.

title: Nike Air Max Triax LE

short_description: The Nike Air Max Triax LE is bringing back the heat. Featuring the same chunky shape and large-volume visible Air unit as the OG, it brings back those sleek, head-turning lines and plush padding that defined '90s style.

short_description: Bridging sport and fashion, the Nike Asuna Crater takes a fresh step toward sustainability. Made from at least 20% recycled material by weight, the design features soft Crater foam underfoot and rugged tread pattern that grips sand, sidewalks and trails. The ultra-plush strap is made from a mixture including some recycled materials while the unique lacing system with toggle offers a quick, customized fit that lets you transition effortlessly between worlds.

short_description: The Nike Air Max 90 LTR stays true to its OG running roots with the iconic Waffle outsole, stitched overlays of smoothed leather and classic, color-accented TPU plates. The monochromatic upper provides versatile styling options while Max Air cushioning adds comfort to your step.

title: Air Max 90 LTR
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: The Nike Air Max 90 LTR stays true to its OG running roots with the iconic Waffle outsole, stitched overlays of smoothed leather and classic, color-accented TPU plates. The monochromatic upper provides versatile styling options while Max Air cushioning adds comfort to your step.

title: Nike Air Force 1 LV8
subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
short_description: Who’s ready to rock? This version of the Nike AF1 brings bold rocking’ style to an everyday favorite. Pops of bright colors and stencil-like graphics encourage you to be fearless in expressing who you are. Plus, the black on the Swoosh designs rubs away to reveal vibrant purple underneath. Talk about a slam dunk!

title: Nike Air Max Thea Mid

Kids can criss-cross the straps (helps them prep for real laces), and it’s done! These are super-duper breathable, flexible and durable—perfect for little ones to walk, run and play.

title: Nike Revolution 6
subtitle: Little Kids' Shoes
short_description: The Nike Revolution 6 is all about versatility for little athletes, from all-day play to anytime wear. With easy straps, kiddos can feel comfy and secure when slipping these on. title: Nike WearAllDay

title: Nike Air Max 90
subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
short_description: Swoosh up your style in the Nike Air Max 90. With Air tuned for kids, foam cushioning and a flexible sole, it’s all about bringing a ‘90s fave to a new generation. Check out the outsole—the specks are there because it's made with about 15% Nike Grind. Then look closer at the mudguard and check out the multi-colored yarn that highlights multicolored Swoosh designs above.

title: Nike Air More Uptempo
subtitle: Little Kids' Shoes
short_description: Put some A-I-R in playtime with the Nike Air More Uptempo. Max Air unit in the heels give kiddos serious cushioning when they run, jump and skip. Soft suede and smooth synthetic leather add durability while oversized branding gives little feet bold style.

title: Nike Air Zoom Pulse
subtitle: Shoes
short_description: Built for and tested by nurses, the Nike Air Zoom Pulse combines cushioning and flexible traction for a comfortable, natural feel that lasts through long shifts on dry and slippery surfaces. The durable design is easy to clean, pull on and take off to keep you ready for the unexpected.

title: Nike Air More Uptempo
subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
short_description: The Nike Air More Uptempo owes it all to Wilson Smith, the designer behind its legendary look. From the big A-I-R on each side to the Air unit underfoot, these kicks blazed a trail on basketball courts in the ‘90s to become a part of Smith’s legacy and Nike’s history. Durable and made to play, this pair honors Smith by weaving details like his signature into the design.

title: Nike React Vision
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: From the D/MS/X collection comes a story of surreal comfort. Layered textures, intricate lines and vivid colors combine in a design influenced by the exaggerated world of our dreams. The React foam and an ultraplush tongue provide dreamlike comfort. Step into your dream—the Nike React Vision.

title: Nike Air Force 1 '07 Premium
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: The radiance lives on in the Nike Air Force 1 ’07 Premium. This b-ball original puts a fresh spin on the legendary style and comfort of the AF1 with crisp leather overlays, a translucent outsole and metallic silver accents. A vibrant pink Swoosh design peeks through the sole, adding head-turning style to your every step.

title: Nike SB Dunk High Pro
subtitle: Skate Shoes
short_description: Varsity vibes never go out of style. The Nike SB Dunk High Pro pairs premium materials with classic color blocking for an iconic look—reimagined for skate. Orange accents finish it off, nodding to the color of Nike's original shoebox from 1971.

title: Nike Blazer Low '77
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Praised by the streets for its classic simplicity and comfort, the Nike Blazer Low '77 returns with a low-profile, old-school hoops look. Celebrating art and DIY style, the paint splatter upper invites you to add your own artistic touch. Or, wear the canvas as is and turn heads with this must-have wardrobe staple's 1-of-a-kind design.

title: Nike Blazer Mid '77 EMB
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Bring your flair for the theatrical and let these wrestling-inspired Blazers do all the talking. The extravagant design includes a cracked leather Swoosh logo, while the championship belt dubrae gives any outfit the edge.

title: Nike Air Max 96 2
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: For the first time, the Air Max 96 2 returns with a 1-1 remake. Bringing back the era-defining shape first imagined by one of Nike's most decorated designers, it's an essential wardrobe staple that boasts a track-inspired look. Plus, the large Nike Air unit keeps the perfect amount of casual while adding lasting comfort.

title: Nike Dunk High 85
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Get back to the past with these coveted retros. Celebrating the '85 original, they bring back the shape that started the off-court revolution. With classic details and throwback hoops flair, they let you channel vintage style back onto the streets. The padded, high-top collar means you can take your game anywhere—in comfort.

title: Nike Court Royale
subtitle: Little Kids' Shoes
short_description: The Nike Court Royale is a slam dunk! Featuring durable materials to keep you moving in comfort, the shoes also have a foam insole for a cushioned, lightweight feel underfoot.

title: Nike Air Max Penny
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Paying tribute to basketball icon Penny Hardaway, the Nike Air Max Penny is a near exact replica of the hoops original. From its jeweled Swoosh to the wing piping on the sides, these original details celebrate both your retro style and a b-ball legend.

title: Nike Air Force 1 Crater
subtitle: Women's Shoes
short_description: The radiance lives on in the Nike Air Force 1 Crater, the b-ball icon that's now made with at least 20% recycled materials by weight. The transparent Swoosh features an array of vibrant materials beneath. The speckles in the rubber outsole are made from Nike Grind, which is recycled waste (i.e., the scraps) from the footwear manufacturing process. It's everything you know best and then some.

title: Nike Air Max INTRLK Lite SE
subtitle: Baby/Toddler Shoes
short_description: Little feet will play all day on cushy Max Air in the Nike Air Max INTRLK Lite SE. Sun-washed colors and rainbow pull tabs celebrate the happy, hopeful messages found in kids' sidewalk chalk art. And don't worry—elastic laces make them super easy to get on and off so playtime never waits.

title: Nike Force 1 LV8
subtitle: Baby/Toddler Shoes
short_description: Lace up the feel-good vibes in the Nike Force 1 LV8, which combines classic AF1 lines with a friendly shout-out and flower graphic. A leather upper brings comfort and durability that's ideal for growing feet.

title: Nike Air Max Penny
subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
short_description: The Nike Air Max Penny pays tribute to a hoops icon with a near-exact replica of the beloved original. The heel tab, support wing, lacing system and even the logo on the back have been maintained for retro style.

title: Nike Blazer Low X
subtitle: Men's Shoes
short_description: Praised by the streets for classic simplicity and comfort, the must-have wardrobe staple just got reimagined. A plush, 3/4-length foam wedge in the midsole pillows your step. A sleek, low-profile tongue feels soft and smooth. Fresh Swoosh branding adds depth and energy. Crisp, tumbled leather and a sleek, low-top design make it easy to style. Meet the Blazer Low X.

title: Nike Air Force 1 LV8 Next Nature
subtitle: Big Kids' Shoes
short_description: The radiance lives on in the Nike Air Force 1 LV8 Next Nature. Made with strong and durable woven poly hemp, these b-ball icons get a vibrant upgrade thanks to a mix of fun, bright colors. Of course, you still get Nike Air cushioning for comfort and the iconic pivot-circle outsole that helped make the ’82 original famous. Plus, the speckled outsole uses Nike Grind—rubber containing at least 13% recycled content.
